node.contents: If `otherClass` is a class name, you should first of all called it with an initial capital `O`. Secondly, you can call only methods which are static directly from a class name without instantiating an object. So, wither you make your `setnumStudents` static (which I doubt is what you really want) or you instantiate an object of type `otherClass` (possibly, `OtherClass`)
